flowchart LR
  upstream[Upstream system<br/>e.g. supplier API]
  sns[SNS topic]
  lambda[Lambda handler<br/>parse + transform]
  raw[S3: raw/<br/>partitioned by source + date]
  staged[S3: staged/<br/>parquet, typed, validated]
  curated[S3: curated/<br/>deduped + joined]
  athena[Athena / Spark<br/>query layer]

  upstream -->|publishes event| sns
  sns -->|triggers| lambda
  lambda -->|write idempotent key| raw
  raw -->|scheduled job| staged
  staged -->|joins, dedup| curated
  curated -->|SQL queries| athena

  classDef store fill:#fff3bf,stroke:#f08c00;
  classDef compute fill:#d3f9d8,stroke:#2f9e44;
  class raw,staged,curated store;
  class lambda,athena compute;
